name: My first Hicetnunc mint
description: I went through many strange stages in my creativity. In addition to working as a muralist, painter, designer, 2D artist, retoucher, making props, I did tattoos. One of them was a catch phrase in Latin I did in 2016 on one’s foot, which has turned into an ultra-promising platform in the eco NFT trend called “Hic Et Nunc” where I’m typing this text right now. Life can take an amazing turns, huh?
